    "description": "Shiprocket invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Digital Marketing Manager at our Vadodara location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Shiprocket:\nShiprocket is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shiprocket!",
